{"tid":1425232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於鐳射筆戰術，有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:44:18.000Z","uid":54857,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a68439f9488f5d25edae52af30967e404cc1f4c5","tid":1425232,"uid":54857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"鐳射筆的確係好有用嘅工具，尤其用嚟擾亂狗隻嘅視覺同慢性扣血。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過</span><br />\n<br />\n最近一兩日都有好多手足係咁射向夢境左右嘅民居住宅，尤其喺深水埗伺服器。當初增加伺服器區域，其中一個好處係令當區街坊受到TG感召而醒覺，好似黃大仙咁。進而班街坊就會喺買餸飲茶時鬧鳩啲癲狗，而唔鬧大家，甚至支持返大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果鐳射筆戰術用咗喺民居住宅，因為有一定騷擾性(唔係都唔會用啦)，變相就會同TG感召嘅威力此消彼長，令啲街坊好難幫我地講說話去遊說其他人。<br />\n<br />\n明白有時可能民居都會出現啲廢中廢老喺度掉嘢或者鳩叫，不過唔建議喺橦大廈好似畫畫咁照，寧願集中一點以免錯傷自己人。 <br />\n<br />\n如果有手足見到類似情況，可以建議佢地去集中debuff啲狗，咁會有效好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：核彈都唔割，但希望核彈唔會錯殺自己友"},{"pid":"bc9b7ad6ab140ee564e5f8e8247bb5de24a1454a","tid":1425232,"uid":54857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:33:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a7646ece9524332d9990bd3c8c31a6417ec74c41","tid":1425232,"uid":54857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"00189cf120040add70391b14423a11597afec16b","tid":1425232,"uid":54857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"94798cda50bcba378eedaf3b664fe30dbd786275","tid":1425232,"uid":54857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:44:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bb63236638b952f492f787cbf8e4bc4003081958","tid":1425232,"uid":54857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}